Package graph

package graph
Provides classes for managing graph structures.

This package includes classes for creating and manipulating graphs, including nodes and edges. It is used to represent topics and agents in a publish-subscribe system.

    Agent
    The Agent interface defines the structure for agent objects in a messaging system.
    BinOpAgent
    The BinOpAgent class implements the Agent interface to perform binary operations on messages received from two subscribed topics and publish the result to a third topic.
